name: Create/Collect
description:
You open your eyes, start the machine, angels are swimming with you.
You click, you make, you wait... awake.. the pressure, the pain, the serenity.
Catch that wave, rise above and beyond. That pump, your senses, rejoice galore.
You search, you find, you collect, you savor.  
Anything else, at this moment, cannot not be known.
You sleep in a daze. Reassess, replenish and explore.
You wake, and without thinking, you want this and more. 
Start the machine.

The endless cycle of HeN life. An ML audio/visual by Adi Oohgaga.
